it.apice.sapere.node.networking.utils.impl This package contains some utility classes for networking handling. 
it.apice.sapere.space This package contains it.apice.sapere.space entities tests.

Classes in it.apice.sapere.api.lsas used by it.apice.sapere.api
LSA
           This interface models an LSA: Live Semantic Annotation.
LSAid
           This interface models an LSA-id which is a unique system-wide key used to identify an LSA.
Property
           A property is a component of an LSA's Semantic Description.
PropertyName
           This interface models a generic name which is valid to identify an LSA property.
SemanticDescription
           A Semantic Description is a collection of properties that are associated to the LSA containing the description.
